Subject: [PATCH] net: can: j1939: j1939_xtp_rx_rts_session_active():
 deactivate session upon receiving the second rts
References: bsc#1234429
Patch-mainline: 6.12.67
Git-commit: 1809c82aa073a11b7d335ae932d81ce51a588a4a

commit 1809c82aa073a11b7d335ae932d81ce51a588a4a upstream.

Since j1939_session_deactivate_activate_next() in j1939_tp_rxtimer() is
called only when the timer is enabled, we need to call
j1939_session_deactivate_activate_next() if we cancelled the timer.
Otherwise, refcount for j1939_session leaks, which will later appear as

| unregister_netdevice: waiting for vcan0 to become free. Usage count = 2.

problem.

